'''本海涅'''（{{lang-en|Ben Heine}}，{{bd|1983年|}}）是一位著名的[[比利时|比利时]]跨界别[[视觉艺术家|视觉艺术家]]<ref>Rebecca Pocklington , [http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/weird-news/3d-artist-ben-heine-walks-2994328 “Artist walks with a tiger and gets held up by a gun in stunning 3D sketches”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/weird-news/3d-artist-ben-heine-walks-2994328 |date=20160917094801 }}  ''Mirror.co.uk'' , 6 January 2014 ,</ref> 和[[音乐制作人|音乐制作人]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.artistup.fr/articles/843/ben-heine-et-le-pouvoir-infini-de-l-imagination |title=“Ben Heine et le pouvoir infini de l'imagination” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818142718/http://www.artistup.fr/articles/843/ben-heine-et-le-pouvoir-infini-de-l-imagination |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Du talent à revendre">{{Cite web |url=http://www.lavenir.net/cnt/dmf20160201_00773327/du-talent-a-revendre |title=“Du talent à revendre” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2017-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225151711/http://www.lavenir.net/cnt/dmf20160201_00773327/du-talent-a-revendre |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。2010年，他的名字因创造出新的艺术形式“铅笔对相机”(Pencil Vs Camera.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2534667/Incredible-3D-pencil-drawings-artist-INSIDE-picture.html |title=“Optical intrusion: Incredible 3D pencil drawings that allow the artist to step INSIDE the picture” ''Dailymail'' ,6 January 2014 |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818231633/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2534667/Incredible-3D-pencil-drawings-artist-INSIDE-picture.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Kate Schneider [http://www.theaustralian.com.au/archive/travel-2015-pre-life/theres-something-sketchy-about-these-images/story-e6frg8ro-1226228309747 “Something sketchy about Ben Heine's 'Pencil vs Camera' images”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/archive/travel-2015-pre-life/theres-something-sketchy-about-these-images/story-e6frg8ro-1226228309747 |date=20200322110107 }} “The Australian” ,23 December 2011</ref> )而被大家知晓。他是技艺娴熟的插图画家和摄影师<ref>[http://neft.media/novosti/v-muzee-izobrazitelnih-iskusstv-proydet-vistavka-bena-hayne-karandash-protiv-kameri “В Музее изобразительных искусств пройдет выставка Бена Хайне”] {{Wayback|url=http://neft.media/novosti/v-muzee-izobrazitelnih-iskusstv-proydet-vistavka-bena-hayne-karandash-protiv-kameri |date=20160815220348 }}  "Карандаш против камеры"</ref> 创作出的众多作品广泛涉及到艺术及设计领域。<ref>[http://techgnotic.deviantart.com/journal/Artist-on-Fire-The-Creative-Juggernaut-Ben-Heine-280184491 “Artist on Fire”] {{Wayback|url=http://techgnotic.deviantart.com/journal/Artist-on-Fire-The-Creative-Juggernaut-Ben-Heine-280184491 |date=20160630111101 }} ‘'Deviant Art''</ref> 他还是新颖艺术系列的创作者比如“数码圆点”(Digital Circlism)<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturepicturegalleries/8398162/Digital-Circlism-portraits-of-celebrities-by-Ben-Heine.html “Digital Circlism: portraits of celebrities by Ben Heine” ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturepicturegalleries/8398162/Digital-Circlism-portraits-of-celebrities-by-Ben-Heine.html |date=20111213054550 }} “Telegraph” ,6 June 2016</ref>和“人体与丙烯”(Flesh and Acrylic).<ref>[http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/news/3993866/artist-Ben-Heine-paints-models-bodies-for-his-new-exhibition.html “Now that's what you call  a BODY of art”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/news/3993866/artist-Ben-Heine-paints-models-bodies-for-his-new-exhibition.html |date=20111213045022 }} “The Sun” ,12 December 2011</ref>

他1983年出生于象牙海岸，现生活与工作于比利时。有新闻专业学位，他的绘画<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1353259/Belgian-artist-Ben-Heine-turns-photos-surreal-landscapes-sketchpad.html “Pencilled in: Artist turns camera images into surreal landscapes with his sketchpad”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1353259/Belgian-artist-Ben-Heine-turns-photos-surreal-landscapes-sketchpad.html |date=20160818230458 }} ''Dailymail'' ,10 February 2011]</ref>，摄影<ref name="lifestyleasia"> Grace Chee, [http://www.lifestyleasia.com/hk/en/culture/art/feature/cocoa-canvas-ben-heine-mixing-chocolate-art/ “Cocoa canvas: Ben Heine on mixing chocolate with art”] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701080805/http://www.lifestyleasia.com/hk/en/culture/art/feature/cocoa-canvas-ben-heine-mixing-chocolate-art/ |date=2016-07-01 }} ,3 February 2015 </ref> 与音乐<ref name="Du talent à revendre"/> 都是自学的。自从2010年他的作品开始出现在欧洲,<ref>Kerry Mcqueeney , [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2041426/Ben-Heine-The-incredible-optical-illusions-created-artists-mix-pencil-camera.html “Pencil vs reality... where do you draw the line? The incredible optical illusions created by artist”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2041426/Ben-Heine-The-incredible-optical-illusions-created-artists-mix-pencil-camera.html |date=20170520003559 }} ''Dailymail'', 26 September 2011</ref>亚洲<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20150204/00296_001.html |title=“Ben Heine朱古力誘畫” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813084343/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20150204/00296_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://unwire.hk/2015/01/25/ben-heine/people-interview/ppl_interview/#!prettyPhoto |title=“領略愛的演化 － 專訪比利時跨界別視覺藝術家 Ben Heine” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2017-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170221110311/https://unwire.hk/2015/01/25/ben-heine/people-interview/ppl_interview/#!prettyPhoto |dead-url=no }}</ref> 及俄罗斯<ref>[http://www.metronews.ru/galerei-i-video/v-moskve-otkryvaetsja-vystavka-bel-gijskogo-hudozhnika-karandash-protiv-kamery/Tpoofq---xqZZaudAEPmOE/ “В Москве открывается выставка бельгийского художника "Карандаш против камеры"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metronews.ru/galerei-i-video/v-moskve-otkryvaetsja-vystavka-bel-gijskogo-hudozhnika-karandash-protiv-kamery/Tpoofq---xqZZaudAEPmOE/ |date=20160629122640 }} ,17 March 2015</ref> 的画廊与博物馆，他的作品已被世界范围内的主要报纸，杂志及书籍广泛刊登。海涅自2009年起永久停止创作政治艺术。<ref name="matele">Nicolas Debatty, [http://www.matele.be/babel-cafe-avec-ben-heine “Babel Café avec Ben Heine”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.matele.be/babel-cafe-avec-ben-heine |date=20171201131549 }}, 20 January 2016</ref> 2012年一个关于他的创作的记录片问世。他有一个儿子和一个女儿。

海涅从2012年开始作曲与制作音乐，他还会打鼓与弹钢琴。<ref name="matele" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://soundcloud.com/benheine |title=“Ben Heine” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2017-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422151633/https://soundcloud.com/benheine |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2013年他拥有了一家音乐工作室。他的第一部音乐专辑“声音漩涡”(Sound Spiral) 于2015年11月问世。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/sound-spiral/id1038125333 |title=“Sound Spiral” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010180246/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/sound-spiral/id1038125333 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 通过这样的职业道路, 海涅成为 [[三星集团|三星]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.inmd.co.kr/portfolio/detail/exhibition-the-universe-of-ben-heine/ |title=“Exhibition: The Universe of Ben Heine” |access-date=2017-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816205405/http://www.inmd.co.kr/portfolio/detail/exhibition-the-universe-of-ben-heine/ |archive-date=2016-08-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和[[马自达|马自达]]<ref name="Design Cars">{{Cite web |url=http://fr.mazda.be/mazda-spirit/design-cars/ben-heine/ |title=“Design Cars” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523164153/http://fr.mazda.be/mazda-spirit/design-cars/ben-heine/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 等著名品牌的代言人。

==早期生平与教育==
本1983出生在象牙海岸的象牙海岸的[[阿比让|阿比让]],在那里他与他的父母和三个姐妹共同渡过了生命中的最初的七年。1990年他们一家搬到比利时的布鲁塞尔。他的父亲是一位商业工程师，母亲是一名编舞和舞蹈老师. 海涅11岁开始学习画画。 在那时他就对视觉艺术产生了极大的兴趣。<ref>[http://www.pomorie.ru/news/v-arhangelke-otkrilas-unikalnaya-vistavka-belgiys “В Архангельске открылась уникальная выставка бельгийского художника - Бена Хайне”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pomorie.ru/news/v-arhangelke-otkrilas-unikalnaya-vistavka-belgiys |date=20160921181832 }}| “ Pomorie.ru”,  3 May 2016</ref>

1998至2006年间，海涅在不同的国家学习，包括象牙海岸，比利时，英国及荷兰。他在布鲁塞尔的Notre Dame de La Trinité上的小学。<ref>[http://mydesignstories.com/pencil-vs-camera-illustrations-ben-heine/  “Pencil Vs Camera: Illustrations by Ben Heine”] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531032330/http://mydesignstories.com/pencil-vs-camera-illustrations-ben-heine/ |date=2016-05-31 }} 3 May 2016</ref>少年时期，他开始练习画画，为音乐配诗及体育运动。<ref>[http://www.photoshop.com/spotlights/ben-heine  “Spotlight Ben Heine”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.photoshop.com/spotlights/ben-heine |date=20170208042917 }}  3 May 2016]</ref>他先后就读于布鲁塞尔自由大学，IHECS<ref>[http://www.ihecs.be/en/actualite/cool-seoul  “Cool, Séoul ! IHECS”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ihecs.be/en/actualite/cool-seoul |date=20180108175012 }} 3 May 2016]</ref>，并于2007年获得[[新闻|新闻]]学学位。本还在 赫斯廷斯艺术与技术学院及荷兰乌特勒支应用科学大学学习艺术史，雕塑及绘画。此外他还专业学习了鼓，非洲鼓及钢琴等乐器的演奏。他的学习及对沟通的热爱让他学会了六种不同的语言有法语，英语，荷兰语，波兰语，西班牙语及俄语。<ref>[https://justimagine-ddoc.com/art/pencil-vs-camera-by-ben-heine/  “ Pencil Vs Camera by BEN HEINE”] {{Wayback|url=https://justimagine-ddoc.com/art/pencil-vs-camera-by-ben-heine/ |date=20160822225827 }}, 3 May 2016]</ref>

2007年到2009年，海涅为谋生做过各种工作，先在比利时的传媒公司做文案，还在布鲁塞尔的多家学校教过语言，甚至还在超市里做过收银员。除了这些工作，本总是把创作放在首位，他每天晚上都坚持画画。<ref>[://t-i.ru/article/new/6150/ “Щедрое творчество Бена Хайне”] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629171510/http://t-i.ru/article/new/6150 |date=2016-06-29 }},  3 May 2016]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ria.ru/moscow/20150618/1076779098.html |title=“Выставка 3D-иллюзий Бена Хайне откроется в московском Планетарии”, 3 May 2016 |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603202103/http://ria.ru/moscow/20150618/1076779098.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

对海涅来说2010是十分重要的一年，那一年，他开始创作他的主要系列作品“铅笔对相机”和“数码圆点”。<ref>[http://www.bruzz.be/nl/nieuws/brusselse-tekenaar-scoort-engeland  “Brusselse tekenaar scoort in Engeland”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bruzz.be/nl/nieuws/brusselse-tekenaar-scoort-engeland |date=20160810030311 }} 3 May 2016]</ref><ref>[http://en.cncnews.cn/news/v_show/44223_Brussels_Accessible_Art_Fair.shtml  “Brussels Accessible Art Fair”] {{Wayback|url=http://en.cncnews.cn/news/v_show/44223_Brussels_Accessible_Art_Fair.shtml |date=20180108064437 }},  3 May 2016]</ref> 从2010年至今，海涅在世界主要的艺术品交易会，博物馆和画廊中展出了他的作品。<ref>[http://www.benheine.com/exhibitions.php?wt=old  “Ben Heine Exhibitions”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.benheine.com/exhibitions.php?wt=old |date=20160603003647 }} “ Тюменские Известия”  3 May 2016]</ref> 自2011年起他还继续发展他的音乐形式。<ref>[http://www.matele.be/babel-cafe-avec-ben-heine  “Babel Café avec Ben Heine”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.matele.be/babel-cafe-avec-ben-heine |date=20171201131549 }}  3 May 2016]</ref>

===影响===
海涅说他是受到了比利时的[[超现实主义|超现实主义]]，<ref>[http://newslite.tv/2011/02/25/pencil-v-camera-the-surreal-ar.html|accessdate=28 March 2011|newspaper=Newslite.tv|date=25 February 2011 “Pencil v Camera: The surreal art of Ben Heine”]{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} [https://web.archive.org/web/20110429114228/http://newslite.tv/2011/02/25/pencil-v-camera-the-surreal-ar.html], 29 April 2011</ref>德国的[[表现主义|表现主义]],<ref>[http://photographershalloffame.blog.com/2011/01/22/the-creative-genius-of-ben-heine-to-boldly-go-where-no-man-has-gone-before/ “The creative genius of Ben Heine:….to boldly go where no man has gone before.!”] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20121129041207/http://photographershalloffame.blog.com/2011/01/22/the-creative-genius-of-ben-heine-to-boldly-go-where-no-man-has-gone-before/ |date=2012-11-29 }}  “Photographers Hall of Fame”, 22 January 2011</ref>美国的波普艺术,<ref>[http://www.mymodernmet.com/profiles/blogs/celebrity-portraits-made-from “ Celebrity Portraits Made from Thousands of Circles”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mymodernmet.com/profiles/blogs/celebrity-portraits-made-from |date=20111018150054 }} “My Modern Metropolis”</ref>和[[社会现实主义|社会现实主义]]<ref>[http://blog.makemycreative.in/2010/07/interview-of-ben-heine-for.html  “Interview of Ben Heine for MakeMyCreative!”] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812152457/http://blog.makemycreative.in/2010/07/interview-of-ben-heine-for.html |date=2011-08-12 }} “Make my Creative”,  5 July 2010</ref>的影响 . 对于海涅Abduzeezo是这样说的: "他的画廊里充满了各种棒极了的东西，他可以自由的在不同的艺术方向间穿行，在每一个方向他都能创造出激动人心的作品。<ref>[http://abduzeedo.com/beautiful-inspiring-artworks-ben-heine  “Beautiful & Inspiring Artworks by Ben Heine”] [https://web.archive.org/web/20110501073111/http://abduzeedo.com/beautiful-inspiring-artworks-ben-heine], 1 May 2011 </ref> 海涅已经在数次采访中解释过他创作背后的理念了。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://benjaminheine.blogspot.com/2006/05/charlie290506-ben-heine.html |title=benjaminheine.blogspot.com – interviews |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2011-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110422181159/http://benjaminheine.blogspot.com/2006/05/charlie290506-ben-heine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==音乐==
海涅2001年开始创造[[电子音乐|电子音乐]], 写歌, 演唱并作曲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spletnik.ru/blogs/pro_zvezd/120316_znakomtes-ben-khayne-ben-heine |title=“Знакомьтесь, Бен Хайне (Ben Heine)” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108174803/http://www.spletnik.ru/blogs/pro_zvezd/120316_znakomtes-ben-khayne-ben-heine |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2012年开始他在比利时拥有了一间音乐工作室。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.artistup.fr/page/BenHeineMusic |title=“Ben Heine Music” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803063245/http://www.artistup.fr/page/BenHeineMusic |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2013年, 海涅的音乐《和你飞》(Fly With You)被载入英国DMS Mesh 1.0收藏音乐集。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.musicsolutions.org.uk/existing-artist-tips/ben-heine/ |title=“Ben Heine” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108062738/http://www.musicsolutions.org.uk/existing-artist-tips/ben-heine/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 从 2013 到2014, 他把主要精力放在了提高他的音乐理论水平与钢琴的练习上。2014年,海涅开始与其他的音乐人及歌手合作。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://soundcloud.com/benheine/warsaw-ben-heine-music-featuring-saxophonist-stephane-pigeon-2016 |title=“Ben Heine” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2017-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520020649/https://soundcloud.com/benheine/warsaw-ben-heine-music-featuring-saxophonist-stephane-pigeon-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年, 海涅的音乐首次在莫斯科天文馆<ref>[http://b-m.info/afisha/ben_khayne_s_karandashom_protiv_kamery_/ “Бен Хайне с карандашом против камеры”] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701091602/http://b-m.info/afisha/ben_khayne_s_karandashom_protiv_kamery_/ |date=2016-07-01 }} ,16 June 2015</ref>公演，并于2016年在阿尔汉格尔斯克国家博物馆<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.news29.ru/novosti/kultura/Bitva_Karandasha_protiv_kamery_razvernjotsja_v_stenah_arhangelskih_Gostinyh_dvorov/47313 |title=“Битва "Карандаша против камеры" развернётся в стенах архангельских Гостиных дворов - Культура - Новости Архангельска” |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2016-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806145731/http://www.news29.ru/novosti/kultura/Bitva_Karandasha_protiv_kamery_razvernjotsja_v_stenah_arhangelskih_Gostinyh_dvorov/47313 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，秋明美术博物馆<ref name="tvkultura.ru">[http://tvkultura.ru/article/show/article_id/147668/ “В Тюмени представили выставку "Карандаш против камеры!" Бена Хайне”] {{Wayback|url=http://tvkultura.ru/article/show/article_id/147668/ |date=20160924205846 }} ,28 January 2016</ref>进行他在俄罗斯的独唱音乐会的巡回演出。<ref>[https://www.ridus.ru/news/188875 “Бен Хайне не сопротивляется гармоничному противостоянию фото и рисунка”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ridus.ru/news/188875 |date=20171001214115 }} ,28 March 2015</ref> 本•海涅的第一个实验性音乐集《声音旋涡》(Sound Spiral)于2015年问世。<ref>[http://www.dlounge.org/2015/09/20/sound-spiral-by-ben-heine-music/ “Sound Spiral by Ben Heine Music”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dlounge.org/2015/09/20/sound-spiral-by-ben-heine-music/ |date=20160805125646 }} ,20 September 2015</ref> 2016年3月, 他的新曲《华莎》(Warsaw), <《我是小丑》(I'm a Clown), 《爱情》(Amour)和《玩玩而已》(It's Just a Play)被维克斯音乐（Wix Music）选中并在美国德州西南偏南音乐节(SXSW music festival)上演出。

==赞助商与画廊==
自2010 到 2013年, 本•海涅与三星照相机合作并成为新摄会的第一位Imagelogger<ref>Alessio Lana, [http://gadget.wired.it/foto/2013/09/11/ben-heine-pencil-vs-camera-quando-la-matita-incontra-la-fotografia-892344.html “Pencil VS Camera, quando la matita incontra la fotografia”] {{Wayback|url=http://gadget.wired.it/foto/2013/09/11/ben-heine-pencil-vs-camera-quando-la-matita-incontra-la-fotografia-892344.html |date=20161012023901 }} | “Wired (magazine)” , 11 September 2013</ref><ref>[http:/samsungcamera.com/news-from-belgium-latest-update-from-ben-heine/ “News from Belgium : Latest Update from Ben Heine” [https://web.archive.org/web/20140402023913/http://samsungcamera.com/news-from-belgium-latest-update-from-ben-heine/],  2 April 2014 </ref> 这个项目由三星运行，为的是请全世界的摄影师测试他们的新相机。本试用了三星最新推出的NX相机和镜头及不同的Galaxy NX镜头。三星还特别为他2012年在里斯本的项目赞助了三星Note 10.1，<ref>[https://news.samsung.com/global/galaxy-note-galaxy-note-ii-and-galaxy-10-1-fusing-art-and-technology “GALAXY Note, GALAXY Note II and GALAXY 10.1: Fusing Art and Technology”] {{Wayback|url=https://news.samsung.com/global/galaxy-note-galaxy-note-ii-and-galaxy-10-1-fusing-art-and-technology |date=20170908155154 }}  “Samsung” ,11 December 2012</ref> 并赞助了他2013年在首尔惠化艺术中心(Hyehwa Art Center)举办的独唱音乐会。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.inmd.co.kr/portfolio/detail/exhibition-the-universe-of-ben-heine/?ckattempt=1 |title=“Exhibition: The Universe of Ben Heine” |access-date=2017-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908155007/http://www.inmd.co.kr/portfolio/detail/exhibition-the-universe-of-ben-heine/?ckattempt=1 |archive-date=2017-09-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

In 2014, 海涅与Chromaluxe合作。<ref>[http://www.chromaluxe-square.com/PBCPPlayer.asp?ID=1488965 “ChromaLuxe Gallery Ben Heine”] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701181227/http://www.chromaluxe-square.com/PBCPPlayer.asp?ID=1488965 |date=2016-07-01 }}</ref> 2015年, 本•海涅又与马自达合作设计了一款汽车并参加各种活动。他成为了马自达在比利时的代言人，为此他到亚特兰大和巴塞罗那为马自达进行相关宣传。<ref name="Design Cars"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/bubobox.campaign/3451/src/index-fr.html |title=“A car is not a piece of art. Or is it?” |access-date=2017-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818150656/https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/bubobox.campaign/3451/src/index-fr.html |archive-date=2016-08-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2016年, 比利时和法国的色域画廊(Colorfield Gallery),俄罗斯的Expomania，英国的艺术运动(The Art Movemen),香港的陈伟霆设计(William Chan Design),韩国的INMD，美国的马尔施泰特画廊(Mahlstedt Gallery)和iCanvas, 德国的科勒设计(Kare Design), 比利时的DCA和Begramoff画廊都展出了海涅的作品。2016年, 海涅作为比利时的影响者之一参加了由三星举办的拥有曙光(OwnTheTwilight)活动，用三星的Galaxy S7 Edge拍摄照片。<ref>[http://www.samsung.com/be_fr/ownthetwilight/ambassador/#/benheineart “Ben Heine”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.samsung.com/be_fr/ownthetwilight/ambassador/#/benheineart |date=20160630040843 }} “Samsung”</ref>

